::Kaiser/The Dragoon::
       Kaiser shrugs his shoulders indolently.  "He says he is the Dragoon, 
and that he would like to speak with you.  That's all I know."  He steps to 
the back of the room and leans against a wall back to his former, calmer, 
darker self.  "He looks like an adequate warrior from here but I'm not 
certain."

       Meanwhile the Dragoon steps forward to stand in front of Tyrael.  "We 
are the Dragoon.  We live only to fight and serve.  We have no affiliation.  
Who may we kill?"  He crosses his arms over his chest and waits for his 
command.

--part1_1dc.910a39b.2be875ac_boundary
